descript.abstract:
This layer contains Lat/Long data along with other oil and gas related information. Symbols represent the surface location of a rig. There may be a delay in actual locations of any specified rig depending on when updated locational data is submitted to the NDIC.
Rig Status: DRLG - Drilling, TDED - Target Depth Reached, MIRU - Moving In/ Rigging Up
descript.purpose: Representation of locations for operating Rigs
